Squawktalk comes to life, and...

Squawktalk: Hey, who's idea was it to make me a bird? I mean, of all things,
a bird? It doesn't make sense! I mean, if it made sense then it wouldn't
have happened!

He transforms into the bird and flies around.

Squawktalk: Wait, on second thought, I LOVE being a bird! WHo else here
thinks that a bird is the best robot mode anyone can have? Seriously!
Gorilla's are cool, too, mr. purple! Hey, mr. purple, I report for duty with
you!

Squalktalk lands next to Beast Box...
